                    <h3 class="h5 mt-4"><i class="bi bi-image me-2"></i> Profile Picture Management</h3>
                    <p>When editing a user, you have several profile picture options:</p>

                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success fs-1"></i>
                                    <h5 class="mt-2">Keep Current</h5>
                                    <p class="small">Maintain existing picture</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <i class="bi bi-upload text-primary fs-1"></i>
                                    <h5 class="mt-2">Upload New</h5>
                                    <p class="small">Upload from computer</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <i class="bi bi-link-45deg text-info fs-1"></i>
                                    <h5 class="mt-2">Use URL</h5>
                                    <p class="small">Link to external image</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-danger fs-1"></i>
                                    <h5 class="mt-2">Remove</h5>
                                    <p class="small">Delete current picture</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Account Security -->
    <div class="row mb-4" id="account-security">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card shadow">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2"></i> Account Security
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Administrators have several tools to manage account security and access.</p>

                    <h3 class="h5 mt-3"><i class="bi bi-lock me-2"></i> Account Locking</h3>

                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card border-warning">
                                <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">When to Lock an Account</div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Suspicious activity detected</li>
                                        <li>Multiple failed login attempts</li>
                                        <li>Violation of platform terms</li>
                                        <li>At user's request (temporary suspension)</li>
                                        <li>During security investigations</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card border-success">
                                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">Unlocking Accounts</div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>To unlock a previously locked account:</p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to the user's profile in User Management</li>
                                        <li>Click the "Unlock Account" button</li>
                                        <li>Confirm the action when prompted</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <p class="small">The user will be able to log in immediately after unlocking.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="h5 mt-3"><i class="bi bi-person-x me-2"></i> Account Deletion</h3>
                    <p>Account deletion is a permanent action that cannot be undone. When a user account is deleted:</p>

                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card bg-danger text-white">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="bi bi-exclamation-octagon me-2"></i> What Gets Deleted</h5>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>User profile and personal information</li>
                                        <li>Login credentials and access</li>
                                        <li>Role assignments and permissions</li>
                                        <li>Direct associations with the user account</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card bg-warning">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i> What Remains</h5>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Public discussions created by the user</li>
                                        <li>Comments posted by the user</li>
                                        <li>Content interactions (likes, etc.)</li>
                                        <li>Anonymized activity logs</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-danger">
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <div class="me-3">
                                <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill display-6"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Important Warning</h4>
                                <p class="mb-0">Always confirm with stakeholders before deleting business user accounts. Consider locking accounts instead of deleting them if there's any chance the account might be needed in the future.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Best Practices -->
    <div class="row mb-4" id="best-practices">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card shadow">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i> Best Practices
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Follow these recommendations for effective user management:</p>

                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card h-100">
                                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2"></i> Security
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Never share business user passwords over email</li>
                                        <li>Use secure channels for credential sharing</li>
                                        <li>Encourage users to change default passwords</li>
